7   import java.lang.annotation.Repeatable;
8   import java.lang.annotation.Retention;
9   import java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy;
10  
11  import net.sourceforge.pmd.typeresolution.testdata.UsesRepeatableAnnotations.Multitude;
12  
13  @Multitude("1")
14  @Multitude("2")
15  @Multitude("3")
16  @Multitude("4")
17  public class UsesRepeatableAnnotations {
18  
19      @Repeatable(Multitudes.class)
20      @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
21      @interface Multitude {
22          String value();
23      }
24  
25      @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
26      @interface Multitudes {
27          Multitude[] value();
28      }

30  }
